result.execSummary:
The defendant Rodney Frisch was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Rodney Frisch is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Rodney Frisch was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
  • Rodney Frisch was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
  • Rodney Frisch was found guilty of Intimidate Victim/Dissuade Complaints [Modifiers: Domestic Abuse], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.44(2).
